OL,3,CVincent Chan: Parents of nursery abuse
OL,4,Cvictims meet Education Secretary
OL,6,FFamilies whose children attended a
OL,7,Fnursery where "prolific" paedophile
OL,8,FVincent Chan worked met with the
OL,9,FEducation Secretary today.
OL,11,FBridget Phillipson heard the families'
OL,12,Frecommendations aimed at ensuring
OL,13,Fearly years settings are closed to
OL,14,Fpredators, and that concerns raised by
OL,15,Fparents and whistleblowers are
OL,16,Fidentified early, escalated
OL,17,Fappropriately, and independently
OL,18,Fscrutinised.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
