PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772618688
OL,3,CVincent Chan: Parents of nursery abuse
OL,4,Cvictims meet Education Secretary
OL,6,FOne of the mothers present at the
OL,7,Fmeeting told ITV News she felt the
OL,8,Fmeeting was "important" in order to
OL,9,F"drive meaningful change."
OL,11,F"It was important to sit down with the
OL,12,Fminister who has the power to drive
OL,13,Fmeaningful change for my children and
OL,14,Ffor every child entrusted to nurseries
OL,15,Fwhile parents are at work. Bridget
OL,16,FPhillipson listened carefully and
OL,17,Fengaged seriously with what we are
OL,18,Fcalling for, practical reforms and
OL,19,Freal accountability to keep children
OL,20,Fsafe," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772618688
OL,3,CVincent Chan: Parents of nursery abuse
OL,4,Cvictims meet Education Secretary
OL,6,FThe families called for an early
OL,7,Fwarning system that would allow
OL,8,Fparents and whistleblowers to report
OL,9,Fconcerns in early years settings to an
OL,10,Findependent external body.
OL,12,FThey are also advocating for CCTV or
OL,13,Fbody-worn video in early years
OL,14,Fsettings, a mandatory two-adult
OL,15,Fsupervision rule for larger settings,
OL,16,Fand stronger safeguards for the use of
OL,17,Fnursery-owned devices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772618688
OL,3,CVincent Chan: Parents of nursery abuse
OL,4,Cvictims meet Education Secretary
OL,6,FPhillipson announced a local child
OL,7,Fsafeguarding practice review in
OL,8,FDecember to "learn every lesson we can
OL,9,Fto make sure that crimes like this are
OL,10,Fguarded against at every step and
OL,11,Fevery stage".
OL,13,FThe education secretary said there
OL,14,Fwere concerns over mandated CCTV and
OL,15,Fthe possibility of other forms of
OL,16,Fchild abuse if footage is misused, and
OL,17,Fhas appointed an expert advisory group
OL,18,Fto develop guidance on the use of CCTV
OL,19,Fwithin the sector.
OL,26,@pD@MOUsD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
