PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772618688
OL,3,CVincent Chan: Parents of nursery abuse
OL,4,Cvictims meet Education Secretary
OL,6,FThe mother ITV News spoke to following
OL,7,Fthe meeting said she had found the
OL,8,Fdepartment for education "receptive
OL,9,Fand supportive".
OL,11,F"It was clear that all of our reforms
OL,12,Fare very much on the table. We left
OL,13,Fwith clear time-bound actions and
OL,14,Fclear answers to our questions," she
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"We look forward to meeting with
OL,18,FOfsted, early years providers and
OL,19,Fexperts in the coming weeks in
OL,20,Fpartnership with the department for
OL,21,Feducation."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
