OL,3,CVincent Chan: Parents of nursery abuse
OL,4,Cvictims meet Education Secretary
OL,6,FVincent Chan carried out a campaign of
OL,7,Fdepraved abuse against children for
OL,8,Fyears. He pleaded guilty to 56 charges
OL,9,Fin December 2025, including five
OL,10,Fcounts of sexual assault by
OL,11,Fpenetration.
OL,13,FHe preyed on children as young as two
OL,14,Fyears old at Bright Horizons nursery
OL,15,Fin North London, where he worked for 7
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
