OL,3,CVincent Chan: Parents of nursery abuse
OL,4,Cvictims meet Education Secretary
OL,6,FChan sexually assaulted children while
OL,7,Fthey slept, filming himself carrying
OL,8,Fout the attacks during naptime, and
OL,9,Flater organised the clips into folders
OL,10,Flabelled with the victim's name.
OL,12,FHe also admitted to taking upskirt
OL,13,Fvideos of girls in class when he
OL,14,Fworked as a teaching assistant in a
OL,15,FNorth London primary school.
OL,17,FHe confessed to spying on girls and
OL,18,Fwomen as they got undressed in their
OL,19,Fbedrooms and used the toilet, and
OL,20,Fsexually assaulting a woman as she
OL,21,Fslept.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
