OL,3,CVincent Chan: Parents of nursery abuse
OL,4,Cvictims meet Education Secretary
OL,6,FThe judge who sentenced Chan to 18
OL,7,Fyears for his crimes in February said
OL,8,Fthe paedophile undertook an "utterly
OL,9,Fwicked, perverse, and depraved"
OL,10,Fcatalogue of abuse that lasted 15
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FJudge Dodd added that the mass of
OL,14,Findecent images of children that Chan
OL,15,Fhad collected, some 26,000, displayed
OL,16,Fa "deep-seated sexual obsession" with
OL,17,Fchildren.
